source.name: Energy Science and Technology Software Center Widget
source.description: This widget is used to find the latest in U.S. Department of Energy-funded scientific and technical software.  The collection also contains selected S&T software from the Nuclear Energy Agency (NEA) of the Organization for Economic Cooperation and Development (OECD).
